article_title: Medina-area man challenges incumbent congressman in GOP primary

article_metadata.description: A real estate agent and distribution company driver in Medina County has launched a Republican primary challenge against Congressman Bob Gibbs, saying he's not really conservative.
article_metadata.author: Robert Wang Repository staff writer
